# Agent Deploy Automation (Kaki Empat v2)

Semua agen **wajib** mengikuti jalur deploy ini. Jangan improvisasi FTP manual atau path docroot salah.

## Stack & docroot (jangan salah)

```
Flutter web → api.kakiempat.com (PHP) → MySQL kakiempa_v2
```

| Target | Docroot FTP (relatif `/home/kakiempa/`) |
|--------|------------------------------------------|
| API/BFF | `api.kakiempat.com/` |
| Owner | `owner.kakiempat.com/` |
| Sitter | `sitter.kakiempat.com/` |
| Admin | `admin.kakiempat.com/` |
| Staging | `staging.kakiempat.com/` |
| WWW | `public_html/` |

**Larangan:** `/public_html/api/` — path itu salah.

## GitHub Actions (utama — hindari blokir IP)

| Workflow | File | Pemicu | Fungsi |
|----------|------|--------|--------|
| Super Charge Backend | `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` | Push `main`/`master` + perubahan `hosting/api.kakiempat.com/**` | Delta FTP backend → `api.kakiempat.com/` + cek `health.php` |
| Deploy Web/API manual | `.github/workflows/deploy-ftp.yml` | Actions → Run workflow | Pilih target: api, owner, sitter, admin, staging, www, owner-and-api |

**Secrets GitHub (wajib):** `FTP_SERVER`, `FTP_USERNAME`, `FTP_PASSWORD`, `FTP_PORT` (21).  
Panduan: `.github/DEPLOY_SECRETS.md`

## Alur kerja agen setelah mengubah kode

### Backend PHP (BFF, katalog layanan, payment, booking)

1. Edit di `hosting/api.kakiempat.com/**`
2. Commit lokal — **jangan** stage file rahasia (`.mysql_v2.php`, `.agent_telemetry_secret`, `hosting.credentials`)
3. `git push` ke `main` atau `master` → Actions **Super Charge** deploy otomatis
4. Verifikasi: `curl https://www.api.kakiempat.com/health.php`

### Flutter web (owner/sitter/admin/www)

1. Build lokal (opsional uji): `.\scripts\deploy_web.ps1 -Target owner -WebRenderer html`
2. Push kode ke GitHub, lalu jalankan workflow **Deploy via FTP** target sesuai subdomain  
   ATAU lokal: `.\scripts\deploy_web.ps1 -Target owner -WebRenderer html -Upload`
3. Money engine penuh: `.\scripts\deploy_owner.ps1 -Layer both -WebRenderer html -Upload`

### Deploy lokal (fallback, bukan utama)

```powershell
.\scripts\deploy_api.ps1
.\scripts\deploy_via_ftp.ps1 -Target api
.\scripts\deploy_api_owner.ps1 -Upload   # hanya owner_v2.php (parsial)
```

**Jangan** upload file satu-per-satu via curl/FTP manual.

## Mata elang — diagnostik mandiri

Setelah deploy atau saat debug produksi:

```http
GET https://www.api.kakiempat.com/health.php
GET https://www.api.kakiempat.com/admin_v2.php?action=agent_health&token=SECRET
```

- Secret server: `.agent_telemetry_secret` (template: `.agent_telemetry_secret.example`) — **hanya di server**, jangan commit
- Metrics: booking hari ini, platform fee, DB status, disk

## Prioritas & batasan

- **Money Engine** (`owner_v2.php`) harus stabil — uji sebelum push besar
- Fitur loyalty/community/referral → di belakang `MvpScope` (`lib/core/config/mvp_scope.dart`)
- Query MySQL baru → manfaatkan INDEX (`created_at`, `status`)
- Stack v2 only — no Firebase/FCM/BaaS (lihat `v2-stack-forbidden-services.mdc`)

## Checklist sebelum selesai task deploy

- [ ] Tidak ada rahasia ter-commit
- [ ] Push/workflow Actions hijau
- [ ] `health.php` → `mysql_ok: true`
- [ ] Subdomain target bisa diakses (owner/admin/dll. sesuai scope)
